#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Interactive console util to toggle macOS launchd services on/off.

Reads labels.txt, shows current disabled state, lets you flip checkboxes,
applies diff with sudo on Enter. Persistent across reboot.

Keys:
  ↑/↓ or j/k   navigate
  PgUp/PgDn    jump 10
  [/]          jump to prev/next section
  space        toggle current
  x            toggle whole section
  s / S        uncheck / check whole section
  a / n        check / uncheck all
  enter        apply changes (prompts sudo)
  r            reload state from system
  q            quit
"""
